snippet.title: Belle Boomerang - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
More information at:
https://gamejolt.com/games/belle/419352

Belle Boomerang is heavily inspired by the shining stars of the 8-bit era. As such, it balances nostalgic elements with a huge dose of originality and charm. Lastly, it's all coated in a layer of beautiful pixel-shaped frosting!

Footage shown in this trailer is not final and is subject to change before release!
